data.description: This home offers unchallenged mountain views, open up the windows at dusk to get the fresh mountain breezes. This lot size of 2.51 acres offers lots of opportunities for growth. With access to the land off of Talley, you can get the most out of this property. With the established out buildings and shop there is plenty of room for all your toys. The Dead end road offers privacy and endless wildlife viewing. The updated ranch style home has beautiful, low maintenance Luxury Vinyl Planks ,  updated lighting   and water heater. This well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath property is just what the doctor ordered. Life in Rye is just the escape you need. Get this one before it's someone else's dream come true.
